---
title: Cajun-Style Bean Stew with Pickled Jalapeños
description: This thick black bean stew is comfort in a bowl! All you need is a giant spoon to tuck into this dish, deeply flavoured with aromatics and brightened by pickled jalapeños.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cajun-style-bean-stew-389febba.jpg
